    <abstract>
      <t>This document proposes two new TLVs within the body of the OSPF
   Router Information (RI) Opaque LSA, called Routable IPv4 Address TLV
   and Routable IPv6 Address TLV.  Here the OSPF means both OSPFv2 and
   OSPFv3.</t>
